{
 "name": "RPlog_Sightseeing_New_Alderaan",
 "title": "Sightseeing in New Alderaan",
 "summary": "With a rare afternoon free, the New Republic pilot Raxis L'ygr explores the plaza of New Alderaan on Ord Mantell and recognizes the entertainer Serenella Jordain lounging in a garden. The two strike up a long, flirtatious conversation, comparing notes on their mutual friend Lance 'Wildman' Dareus -- whom Serenella, it emerges, has just married. She teases the bashful pilot relentlessly, proposing he guest-star as a male stripper aboard her all-female cruise ship the Rancor and demanding an impromptu audition, to his flustered embarrassment. They swap stories about their hometowns, the Imperials, and Lance's brooding mood before Serenella departs to meet her sister, leaving Raxis her card and a kiss on the cheek as he shakes his head at the whole strange encounter.",
